UPDATE courses SET
    course_description = '<div class=\"section--l section--narrow section rich-text elevator__target\" data-elevator-title=\"Overview\" data-student-type=\"both\" id=\"overview\"> <div class=\"section__content\"> <h2>Overview</p> <div class=\"spaced-top copy--intro section--bottom-l block block-layout-builder block-field-blockcdu-coursecdu-coursecourse-overview show-more\" data-once=\"cduShowMore\" data-show-more=\"400\" style=\"height: 400px;\"><p>Step into the world of modern business leadership with the Graduate Certificate in Business. This dynamic program equips you with the essential knowledge and practical skills needed to navigate today"s evolving business landscape with confidence and expertise.</p><p>Designed for professionals looking to enhance their business acumen, this course explores strategic decision-making, leadership, financial literacy, and organisational management. You will learn how to drive business success while balancing operational efficiency and stakeholder engagement.</p><p>Whether you"re seeking to upskill, pivot careers, or lay the foundation for further study, this course offers a flexible and engaging learning experience tailored to your professional ambitions.</p><p>Completion of this course provides a pathway into the Master of Business Administration, allowing you to continue expanding your expertise and career opportunities.</p><p><br/><br/></p><div class=\"show-more__action\"><button class=\"button button--primary-reverse button--icon button--right icon--chevron-down\" role=\"none\">Show more</button></div></div><details class=\"accordion accordion--divided\" data-once=\"webform-details-save\" data-student-type=\"both\"><summary class=\"accordion__toggle\" data-once=\"webform-details-summary-save\" id=\"accordion-career-opportunities\"><p style="font-weight: bold;"> Career opportunities </p><span class=\"button button--small button--icon-only\"></span></summary><div class=\"accordion__content rich-text rich-text--contained\"><p>